C1016: Brake Light Switch Circuit Performance
</emph>
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Brake light switch ON signal is detected for more than specified time while vehicle running with accelerator pedal depressed.
</ptxt>
</item>
